OL,5, The Specials' frontman Terry Hall had  
OL,6, been diagnosed with cancer shortly     
OL,7, before his death this week at the age  
OL,8, of 63, his bandmate has confirmed.     
OL,10,FBassist Horace Panter gave a moving    
OL,11,Faccount of his friend's final days     
OL,12,Frevealing they had planned to record a 
OL,13,Fnew album in November before Hall was  
OL,14,Ftaken ill with a suspected stomach bug.
OL,16,FIt later transpired to be pancreatic   
OL,17,Fcancer, which had spread to his liver. 
OL,19,FInitial treatment went well, but Hall  
OL,20,Fbegan to fade in December, Panter said.
